text: Emily DiDonato (born February 24, 1991) is an American model. She has appeared in advertisements for Miu Miu, Oscar de la Renta, Giorgio Armani, Calvin Klein, Trussardi, Ralph Lauren, Just Cavalli, Missoni, Elie Tahari, Longchamp, Nicole Farhi, Aldo, Gap, Juicy Couture, and Guess. ==References== ==Other websites== * Vogue's "The Scene": The September Issue premier gallery Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Models from New York (state)
title: Emily DiDonato
